  <div class="body_text" itemprop="description">
    <p><strong>Arrows</strong> is the lead single from Fences' new album <strong>Lesser Oceans</strong>. <em>Arrows</em> features rapper Macklemore and produced Ryan Lewis. Straight out of Seattle.</p>

